top_src","label":"ggxNsKpoSDU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxNsKpoSDU_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggxNsKpoSDU_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_22.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gghcfB2hOZT_text","label":"gghcfB2hOZT_text","default":"How much"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFg_OXTC6p_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggFg_OXTC6p_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_22.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxujJ1DGpq_text","label":"ggxujJ1DGpq_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>How much</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmVplSz10k_text","label":"ggmVplSz10k_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">2–3 drops mixed into your regular moisturiser in the palm of your hand. Blend together, then apply evenly to your face, neck, and jawline.</span><br>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">One bottle lasts around 30 days — more or less depending on how often you apply and how much colour you want.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_20.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq-GTtAeFx_text","label":"ggq-GTtAeFx_text","default":"How often"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxWR4THRcy_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggxWR4THRcy_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_20.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN1upZ9Ekk_text","label":"ggN1upZ9Ekk_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>How often</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJZXEE3Zjb_text","label":"ggJZXEE3Zjb_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Start every 2–3 nights. That's enough to build colour without overdoing it. Once you see where you land, adjust — more frequent if you want darker, less if the result already works for you. Find what works and stick with it.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUXjSIs8Lw_text","label":"ggUXjSIs8Lw_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">What To Expect</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJkbrWCf47_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJkbrWCf47_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/30ml_Self_Tanning_Creative_render_1.0.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEEL3r9OyE_text","label":"ggEEL3r9OyE_text","default":"You apply at night, go to bed. In the morning you wash your face as normal — the colour stays. You go from pale to having actual colour.&nbsp;<br><br>Not a tan from a beach holiday, but a healthy, natural tone that makes you look like you're doing fine.<br>&nbsp;That colour holds for 2–3 days. Then it starts to fade. That's when you reapply.<br>&nbsp;No smell. No transfer on the pillow. No one knows why you look better — they just do."}],
